    <title type="html"><![CDATA[GitHub + Octopress == Geek's Blog]]></title>
    <link href="http://luoluo.github.com/blog/2012/03/25/github-plus-octopress-equals-equals-geeks-blog"/>
    <updated>2012-03-25T03:19:00+08:00</updated>
