<span class='line-number'>9</span>
<span class='line-number'>10</span>
<span class='line-number'>11</span>
<span class='line-number'>12</span>
<span class='line-number'>13</span>
<span class='line-number'>14</span>
<span class='line-number'>15</span>
<span class='line-number'>16</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>Generating Site with Jekyll
</span><span class='line'>unchanged sass/screen.scss
</span><span class='line'>Configuration from /home/lo/blog/octopress/"config.yml"
</span><span class='line'>/home/lo/.rvm/rubies/ruby-1.9.2-p290/lib/ruby/1.9.1/net/https.rb:92:in &lt;code>require': no such file to load -- openssl (LoadError)
</span><span class='line'>from /home/lo/.rvm/rubies/ruby-1.9.2-p290/lib/ruby/1.9.1/net/https.rb:92:in&lt;/code>'
</span><span class='line'>from /home/lo/blog/octopress/plugins/gist_tag.rb:10:in &lt;code>require'
</span><span class='line'>from /home/lo/blog/octopress/plugins/gist_tag.rb:10:in&lt;/code>'
</span><span class='line'>from /home/lo/.rvm/gems/ruby-1.9.2-p290/gems/jekyll-0.11.0/lib/jekyll/site.rb:76:in &lt;code>require'
</span><span class='line'>from /home/lo/.rvm/gems/ruby-1.9.2-p290/gems/jekyll-0.11.0/lib/jekyll/site.rb:76:in&lt;/code>block in setup'
</span><span class='line'>from /home/lo/.rvm/gems/ruby-1.9.2-p290/gems/jekyll-0.11.0/lib/jekyll/site.rb:75:in &lt;code>each'
</span><span class='line'>from /home/lo/.rvm/gems/ruby-1.9.2-p290/gems/jekyll-0.11.0/lib/jekyll/site.rb:75:in&lt;/code>setup'
</span><span class='line'>from /home/lo/.rvm/gems/ruby-1.9.2-p290/gems/jekyll-0.11.0/lib/jekyll/site.rb:30:in &lt;code>initialize'
</span><span class='line'>from /home/lo/.rvm/gems/ruby-1.9.2-p290/gems/jekyll-0.11.0/bin/jekyll:224:in&lt;/code>new'
</span><span class='line'>from /home/lo/.rvm/gems/ruby-1.9.2-p290/gems/jekyll-0.11.0/bin/jekyll:224:in &lt;code>'
</span><span class='line'>from /home/lo/.rvm/gems/ruby-1.9.2-p290/bin/jekyll:19:in&lt;/code>load'
</span><span class='line'>from /home/lo/.rvm/gems/ruby-1.9.2-p290/bin/jekyll:19:in `'</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>
卡了半天最后还是十分感谢互联网的Hackers，让我从泥潭中巴腿而出。解决方案就是修复openssl:
<div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>sudo apt-get install libssl-dev
</span><span class='line'>cd ext/openssl&lt;/p>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;p>Run the command one after the others.
</span><span class='line'>ruby extconf.rb
</span><span class='line'>make
</span><span class='line'>sudo make install</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>

<p>然后就神奇的AC了。 原网址:<a href="http://blog.dhavalparikh.co.in/2011/10/solve-no-such-file-to-load-openssl-error/
" title="http://blog.dhavalparikh.co.in/2011/10/solve-no-such-file-to-load-openssl-error/
">http://blog.dhavalparikh.co.in/2011/10/solve-no-such-file-to-load-openssl-error/
</a></p>

<p>3.如何在linux系统中找到以个文件或文件夹，这里真正的使用了FIND命令，感觉神轻气爽.具体的FIND使用规则：man find 好点。</p>

